    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to analyze the Chime manager application module"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/3.0%20Chime%20Manager/1111.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/3.0 Chime Manager/1111.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Chime Manager deployment"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Chime Manager decides which chime to play based on"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "CAN messages",
        "Action messages from HMI application",
        "Chime Producer status and",
        "Priority of Chime event"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Chime manager after deciding which chime to play, will send request to Chime producer in SoC side."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Chime producer will load the audio file based on Chime id and request Audio diver to play the Chime"
    },
    {
